  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Shelter Assistance to Crisis-Affected Populations in the Kouritenga Province, Center-East Region, of Burkina Faso</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Given the humanitarian situation and the continuous rise of vulnerabilities in Burkina Faso, IOM&apos;s response seeks to improve humanitarian assistance to internally displaced persons and host communities in Burkina Faso through enhanced shelter solutions, that intend to maximize the impact of assistance provided through this project by distributing either one of the two types of shelter support - emergency shelter kits, or shelter rehabilitation/ improvement kits, as well as a standard non-food items kit to the same beneficiary households.</narrative>
  </description>
